caption: We had a blast. I’m very thankful for having the best subscribers. Who else meets their subs? And takes them to a country club for a round of golf? I do. And will do it again. OC meet up soon. Next year I plan on NYC, Seattle, SF, Houston, Dallas, Hawaii, Miami, DMV, London. Thank you everyone. I took a 9 day social media break, but I wanted yall to know I talk to yall more than anyone else these days. Appreciate the love.
